@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend
participant DesignEngine
participant Storage (S3/CDN)

User -> Frontend: Request 2D View
Frontend -> DesignEngine: POST /design/2d/render
DesignEngine -> Storage: Check cache
alt cached
    Storage --> Frontend: Return cached asset URL
else not cached
    DesignEngine -> DesignEngine: Generate 2D asset
    DesignEngine -> Storage: Store rendered asset (S3)
    Storage --> Frontend: Return asset URL
end

User -> Frontend: Request 3D View
Frontend -> DesignEngine: GET /design/3d/{configurationId}
DesignEngine -> Storage: Return manifest & signed URLs
Frontend -> Storage: Fetch models (glTF/GLB)
Frontend -> Frontend: Load Three.js scene
@enduml